data.title: STA: Croatia's PM Announces Arbitration on Border with Slovenia
data.meta_description: Croatian Prime Minister Ivica Racan announced Monday that he will request that Croatia's parliament, Sabor, seek international arbitration on the resolution of the border between Slovenia and Croatia.
